3. Gaussian Mixture Models (GMM) Clustering
Notebook: https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1ChydWgSoieaYCyF7DN2BmSe9lT-_6CWl
The notebook explains Gaussian Mixture Models (GMM) for clustering.

Shows probabilistic cluster assignments.
Evaluates clusters using metrics like AIC (Akaike Information Criterion) and BIC (Bayesian Information Criterion).
4. DBSCAN Clustering with PyCaret
