7. Document Clustering with LLM Embeddings
Notebook: https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1jqApv3koe3pC15YjJmHD_4KAjduyS6EW
The notebook demonstrates clustering of documents using state-of-the-art embeddings (e.g., Sentence Transformers).

