Silhouette scores are used to evaluate clustering quality.
8. Image Clustering Using ImageBind Embeddings
Notebook: https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1yZzxOuOB08TqURVHu6wFZJILXZuW8ivf
This notebook performs clustering of images using embeddings from Meta’s ImageBind model.

Explores cross-modality embeddings for clustering images alongside other data types.
Visualization techniques like t-SNE are included for better interpretation.
9. Audio Clustering with ImageBind Embeddings
Notebook: https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1VtEkJDmFEfB-OMnx91x_nAH4Bj2eEuVG
This notebook clusters audio files using embeddings from the ImageBind model.

Applies K-Means clustering to audio embeddings.
Visualizes results using t-SNE and waveform plots.
Common Evaluation Metrics
Inertia and Silhouette Scores: Evaluate clustering performance.
Visualization Techniques: Utilize t-SNE, PCA, dendrograms, and heatmaps for better understanding.
Probabilistic Measures: Assess cluster likelihoods and anomalies in methods like GMM and anomaly detection.
How to Run
Open the desired notebook on Google Colab.
Follow the step-by-step instructions provided in the notebook.
Modify the code to experiment with different datasets or configurations as needed.

